The '''Melon''' is a [[Fruits|fruit]] [[Crops|crop]] that grows from [[Melon Seeds]] after 12 days.  Melon is one of only three crops that can grow into a [[Crops#Giant Crops|giant crop]].

==Stages==
Melons can become a [[Crops#Giant Crops|Giant Crop]].
